<view class="page-shell"><view class="hero-block"><text class="hero-kicker">袋鼠旅客通</text><view class="hero-title">账号绑定</view><view class="hero-subtitle">首次绑定后，后续会按微信身份直接登录，数据权限与后台保持一致。</view></view><view class="surface-card panel"><view class="panel-title">绑定现有 CRM 账号</view><view class="panel-copy">请输入当前使用中的 CRM 账号和密码，完成后即可进入移动客户工作台。</view><view class="field-block"><text class="field-label">账号</text><input class="input" placeholder="请输入 CRM 用户名" value="{{username}}" data-field="username" bindinput="handleInput" /></view><view class="field-block"><text class="field-label">密码</text><input class="input" password="true" placeholder="请输入 CRM 密码" value="{{password}}" data-field="password" bindinput="handleInput" /><view class="field-hint">仅首次需要绑定一次，后续将优先使用微信身份登录。</view></view><view class="field-block"><button class="primary-btn" loading="{{submitting}}" bindtap="handleBind">绑定并进入工作台</button></view></view></view>